  Kinetic (Delta T^0):                   0.940608230991650         25.5953           590.24          2469.57
  Delta V^Pauli Coulomb:                -0.597191238226042        -16.2504          -374.74         -1567.93
  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -0.208728326746806         -5.6798          -130.98          -548.02
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.059105768308005          1.6083            37.09           155.18
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.033010245335891         -0.8983           -20.71           -86.67
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
  Total Pauli Repulsion:                 0.160784188990915          4.3752           100.89           422.14
 (Total Pauli Repulsion =
  Delta E^Pauli in BB paper)

